&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Define the strategic vision for Anthropic&#39;s Microsoft partnership, including annual business planning, multi-year revenue targets, joint roadmap development, and executive-level operational cadences (MBRs, QBRs)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Build and lead a high-performing team, scaling to 6-8 people in the first year with international coverage across EMEA and APAC — with potential to grow significantly as the partnership matures&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Establish and own executive relationships across Microsoft&#39;s field organization, Azure leadership, and product teams at the most senior levels&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Drive partner-sourced and partner-influenced revenue from inception toward a multi-billion-dollar annual run rate, building forecasting models and pipeline management across Strategic, Major, and Enterprise accounts&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Develop and track field activation metrics — driving measurable engagement from Microsoft sellers and solutions architects on Claude opportunities&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Partner cross-functionally with Product, Engineering, Trust &amp;amp; Safety, and Legal to ensure successful integration and deployment of Claude across Microsoft&#39;s ecosystem&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Create scalable co-selling motions, enablement programs, and joint customer engagement frameworks&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Represent Anthropic in high-stakes executive meetings and strategic negotiations with Microsoft leadership&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Collaborate with GSI/SI partnerships (Accenture, Deloitte, etc.) on cloud-influenced enterprise deals&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 class=&quot;heading&quot;&gt;You may be a good fit if you have:&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;15+ years of experience in partnerships, business development, or GTM leadership at technology companies, with deep experience managing strategic cloud provider relationships at scale&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Experience building hyperscaler partnerships to billions of dollars in revenue — ideally having transformed competitive dynamics into strategic alignment&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Proven track record building and scaling teams in high-growth environments, from early stages through significant organizational growth&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Deep understanding of enterprise cloud services, AI/ML market dynamics, and the Microsoft ecosystem specifically&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Exceptional executive presence and the ability to build trusted relationships with the most senior leaders across complex, matrixed organizations&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Strong business acumen paired with technical credibility — you can engage with solutions architects and hold your own in discussions about AI capabilities and enterprise deployment&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Comfort with ambiguity and rapid iteration; you can build an organization and its processes from scratch while delivering results in parallel&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Comfort with rigorous pipeline management, partner activation metrics, and data-driven operating rhythms&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 class=&quot;heading&quot;&gt;Strong candidates may also have:&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Direct experience at Microsoft in senior BD, partnership, or GTM leadership roles&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Track record scaling cloud or AI partnerships at a major ISV (Snowflake, Databricks, MongoDB, Confluent, or similar)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Experience navigating multi-cloud partnership dynamics where partners are simultaneously competitors&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Established relationships within Microsoft&#39;s senior field organization and partner ecosystem&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;International GTM experience, particularly in APAC or EMEA markets&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Board-level or executive advisory experience in technology or growth-stage companies&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
